title: Don Knotts-The_Love_God?
description:
The Love God? 
Directed by Nat Hiken 
Produced by Edward Montagne 
Written by Nat Hiken 
Starring Don Knotts
Anne Francis 
Music by Vic Mizzy 
Cinematography William Margulies 
Editing by Sam E. Waxman 
Distributed by Universal Pictures 
Release date(s)  August 1969 
Running time 101 min. 
Country  United States 
Language English 
IMDb 
The Love God? (1969) is a Universal Pictures feature film starring Don Knotts. The film was written and directed by Nat Hiken, who died after it was shot but before it was released in theaters.





[edit] Cast and characters
Don Knotts - Abner Audubon Peacock IV
